Technology & Innovation: Understand our Investments - Petrobras

















Português
Petrobras WorldwideAccess to informationContact UsOmbudsmanDenouncement Channel




Petrobras


Business ChannelsInvestorsPress
Navegação

Home >
	Our Activities > Technology & Innovation






Technology & Innovation
	Technological innovation and development are the mainstay of all our activities. We are only able to overcome our challenges and gear up for the future because we have great researchers and technological resources that allow us to anticipate scenarios, diversify power generation, improve our products, and make our business more and more sustainable.

For the pioneering technologies we developed with partners and suppliers, we were granted in 2015, for the third time, the OTC Distinguished Achievement Award for Companies, Organizations, and Institutions – the highest technology recognition an oil company can get as an offshore operator.

	Cenpes

	Our Research and Development activities are centralized at the Leopoldo Américo Miguez de Mello Research & Development Center (Cenpes), in Rio de Janeiro. Occupying a total area of 300,000 square meters, it is one of the world's most important applied research complexes. Besides advanced laboratories, it has simulation and process immersion rooms of the energy industry.

AnteriorPróximaVer imagemVer imagemVer imagemVer imagemVer imagemVer imagemVer imagemPróximos itensIntens AnterioresNetwork Technology
	We have developed a new technological partnership model with universities and research institutes that work in collaborative networks. These partnerships include the creation of cutting-edge laboratories, training researchers and project development.

Get to know the thematic networks and their goals (in portuguese).







