	About Us > The Petrobras Brand






The Petrobras Brand
	A company's brand or symbol is the outcome of rigorous branding and visual communication studies conducted by strategy, marketing, and design professionals.

	The goal is to secure a unique personality and a distinctive image for the company. At Petrobras, we work on brand management constantly, as we consider it an increasingly important strategic asset in order for us to achieve our growth and internationalization goals.

