 produces oil and natural gas.  The Company refines, markets, and supplies oil products.  Petrobras operates oil tankers, distribution pipelines, marine, river and lake terminals, thermal power plants, fertilizer plants, and petrochemical units.  The Company operates in South America and elsewhere around the world.    Address  Av Republica do Chile 65CentroRio De Janeiro, RJ 20035-900Brazil   Phone  55-21-3224-2040   Website   www.petrobras.com.br     Executives Board Members    Pedro Pullen Parente  Chief Executive Officer    Ivan De Souza Monteiro  CFO/Dir:Investor Relations    Joao Adalberto Elek  Exec Dir:Governance & Risk    Roberto Moro  Exec Dir:Production Dev & Tech    Hugo Repsold  Exec Dir:Corp Affairs     Show More         
